#. Tag: title
#: x11_fonts.xml:556 x11_fonts.xml:841
#, no-c-format
msgid "Aliases and Family Name Substitutions"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: x11_fonts.xml:559
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule 1"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#: x11_fonts.xml:561
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;alias&gt;\n"
" &lt;family&gt;Alegreya SC&lt;/family&gt;\n"
" &lt;default&gt;\n"
"  &lt;family&gt;serif&lt;/family&gt;\n"
" &lt;/default&gt;\n"
"&lt;/alias&gt;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: x11_fonts.xml:565
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule 2"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#: x11_fonts.xml:567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;alias&gt;\n"
" &lt;family&gt;serif&lt;/family&gt;\n"
" &lt;prefer&gt;\n"
"  &lt;family&gt;Droid Serif&lt;/family&gt;\n"
" &lt;/prefer&gt;\n"
"&lt;/alias&gt;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: x11_fonts.xml:571
#, no-c-format
msgid "Rule 3"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: screen
#: x11_fonts.xml:573
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;alias&gt;\n"
" &lt;family&gt;serif&lt;/family&gt;\n"
" &lt;accept&gt;\n"
"  &lt;family&gt;STIXGeneral&lt;/family&gt;\n"
" &lt;/accept&gt;\n"
"&lt;/alias&gt;"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: x11_fonts.xml:578
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The rules from <xref linkend=\"ex.x11.fontsys.fontconfig.aliases1\"/> create "
"a <emphasis>prioritized family list</emphasis> (PFL). Depending on the "
"element, different actions are performed:"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: x11_fonts.xml:585
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>&lt;default&gt;</literal> from"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: x11_fonts.xml:589
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This rule adds a <literal>serif</literal> family name <emphasis>at the end</"
"emphasis> of the PFL."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: x11_fonts.xml:596
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>&lt;prefer&gt;</literal> from"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: x11_fonts.xml:600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This rule adds <quote>Droid Serif</quote> <emphasis>just before</emphasis> "
"the first occurrence of <literal>serif</literal> in the PFL, whenever "
"<literal>Alegreya SC</literal> is present in PFL."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: term
#: x11_fonts.xml:608
#, no-c-format
msgid "<literal>&lt;accept&gt;</literal> from"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: x11_fonts.xml:611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This rule adds a <quote>STIXGeneral</quote> family name <emphasis>just "
"after</emphasis> the first occurrence of the <literal>serif</literal> family "
"name in the PFL."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: x11_fonts.xml:619
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Putting this together, when snippets occur in the order <xref linkend=\"vle."
"x11.fontsys.example.alias.default\"/> - <xref linkend=\"vle.x11.fontsys."
"example.alias.prefer\"/> - <xref linkend=\"vle.x11.fontsys.example.alias."
"accept\"/> and the user requests <quote>Alegreya SC</quote>, then the PFL is "
"created as depicted in <xref linkend=\"tab.x11.fontsys.example.alias\"/>."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: x11_fonts.xml:628
#, no-c-format
msgid "Generating PFL from Fontconfig rules"
msgstr ""

